<body>
  <h1>⛑️ Quick First Aid Tips</h1>
  <div class="tip">
    <h2>🫀 CPR</h2>
    <p>1. Check responsiveness.<br>
       2. Call for help.<br>
       3. Start chest compressions – 100–120 per minute.<br>
       4. Give rescue breaths if trained.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="tip">
    <h2>🩸 Bleeding</h2>
    <p>1. Apply pressure with cloth.<br>
       2. Keep injured part raised.<br>
       3. Don’t remove soaked cloth – add more layers.<br>
       4. Call emergency services.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="tip">
    <h2>😮‍💨 Choking</h2>
    <p>1. Ask if they can speak.<br>
       2. Give 5 back blows between shoulder blades.<br>
       3. Follow with 5 abdominal thrusts.<br>
       4. Repeat if needed.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
